About Me

Welcome to my world of software engineering and design!

As an experienced lead software engineer, I've had the privilege of collaborating with diverse clients from around the globe and this has helped me with insights on what it takes to run a successful project. My commitment for attention to details and passion for processes have amassed me with a wealth of experience for working in agile environments.

{" "} With a passion for elegant design and a dedication to open source, I strive to create cutting-edge solutions that merge functionality and aesthetics seamlessly. But it doesn't stop there. I believe in the power of connections and the beauty of shared experiences. I'm always eager to meet new people from all corners of the world, to exchange ideas, and to embark on exciting projects together. Let's create something extraordinary and leave a lasting impact on the global tech community!

{" "} Feel free to say hi, ask questions, or simply share your thoughts. Let's build meaningful connections, share knowledge, and create a vibrant community together. Looking forward to hearing from you and embarking on this exciting journey of growth and collaboration!

What am currently doing

Updated June, 2023
Nothing much going on. I spend most of my time crafting tailored commercial software solutions for paid clients and my start up as am currently building software products that am hoping to launch soon! Generating absolutely high quality and first-class output truly means the world to me.

I recently started a dedicated workout routine - early evening and sometimes even morning workouts, and eating vegetables and fruits - nourishing my body with healthy choices. It's been nice this far and I intend to improve and uphold the discipline going forward as it is helping me achieve peak performance.
